task.en: Help me change the icon to a filled star. Don't modify other things.

pre_command: osascript -e 'tell application "Xcode" to close windows' && rm -rf /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp && cp -r /Users/ec2-user/Benchmark_Backup/BenchmarkApp /Users/ec2-user/Documents && cd /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp && git checkout 5ba51e8 && open -a Xcode /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp
in_process: osascript -e 'display dialog "Change icon to filled star, please click here!" with title "Shortcut" buttons {"Cancel", "OK"} default button "OK"'
grading_command: cat /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp/BenchmarkApp/ContentView.swift | sed -e 's|//.*||' -e 's|/\*[^*]*\*+\([^/]*\*/\)| |g' -e 's|/\*.*||' -e 's|.*\*/||' | tr -d '\n' | tr -d ' ' | grep -q 'structContentView:View{varbody:someView{VStack{Image(systemName:"star.fill").imageScale(.large).foregroundStyle(.tint)Text("Hello,world!")}.padding()}}' && echo "True" || echo "False"
